actual = FlairPipeline().process(text, lang='multi', fast=True,
    use_embeddings='default', char_embeddings=False, bpe_size=0)
assert all(map(lambda t: t['embeddings'][0]['model'] ==
    'Flair glove,multi-forward,multi-backward', actual['documents'][1][
    'tokenList'].values())), actual['documents'][1]['tokenList'][1][
    'embeddings'][0]['model']
